# HSOC — Security Operations Center

> Part of the [HMIND Platform](../README.md)

---

## Overview

HSOC is the live security monitoring module of HMIND. It aggregates data from three independent security systems (Wazuh, Zabbix, OpenVAS), normalizes everything into a unified schema, and presents it in a single dashboard with AI-driven analysis per alert, vulnerability, and host.

