## AI Explanation Flow

```
Analyst clicks "Explain" on an alert
              │
              ▼
POST /api/hsoc/explain
{ "type": "alert", "id": 142 }
              │
              ▼
Backend fetches:
  - alert raw JSON
  - last 5 events from same host
              │
              ▼
Prompt built:
  "You are a security analyst. Explain this alert.
   What triggered it, what the attacker may have done,
   recommended response.
   Alert: {raw}
   Host history: {last_5_events}"
              │
              ▼
Groq API → response stored in hsoc_alerts.ai_analysis
              │
              ▼
Returned to dashboard + cached for future views
```

